parameters:
\SE[5]Huh, Vita...? It's unusual for you to be awake at this
hour. \SE[1]What's wrong? Did you have trouble sleeping?

\SE[2]Hmm.... Because I have the crime of being left behind....
\SE[3]I was thinking of executing a little punishment of
storytelling....

\SE[8] The cream puff wasn't very delicious, was it...? \!\SE[23]
I'm sorry... I'm worried that I'm burdening Tita too much...
\!\SE[11] I had no choice but to rely on Vita...

\SE[16]Hmm... I lied. Well, I'm not angry or anything...
\SE[51]The cream puff was delicious. \SE[4]I also had fun keeping
watch with Tita.

\SE[3]The 'punishment of storytelling' is just because I want to
talk.... \SE[1]Feel free to accept the punishment.

\SE[9]Oh... you're trying to hide your embarrassment in a
complicated way... \!\SE[1]I see. A story... Shall we? \.It's
late at night, so just for a little while... \.okay?

\SE[5]... What's wrong, Vita? \SE[1] Did you feel like being a
spoiled child?

\SE[21]Ah, I see. You've become energetic, huh? \SE[3]So, it was
a lie that you wanted to have a storytelling session.

\SE[46]... No, it's not me. It's better for Laura to be the
spoiled child... \SE[9] Not me, but Laura.

\SE[58]Laura seemed to be forcing herself and looked in pain...
so \SE[57]I'm just staying by her side... that's all.

\SE[23]That's not true.... \SE[56]I'm not pushing myself... not
at all....

\SE[70]Well then, that's fine. \!\SE[51]It's just because I feel
lonely.... \.I'm just using Laura as a body pillow....

\SE[56]Laura... you're not alone, you know? \SE[39]I feel the
same way... and Vega too, I'm sure. \SE[62]And of course, Tita...
and everyone else too...

\SE[44]So please... let's do our best together... \SE[45]Don't
bear it all alone...

\SE[58]... I just wanted to say that. \!\SE[63]Mmm... sorry. Was
it unnecessary meddling...?

\SE[15]If I were to stick close to Laura... \SE[52]Well, you
know... I would start feeling... excited....

\SE[39]...Hmph! Enough...! \SE[55]What was with the atmosphere
just now...!

\SE[68]T-That's not fair...! \SE[17]Because it's not Laura's
fault...! She's teasing with her plump butt and seducing us with
such revealing clothes...!!

\SE[46]Hey, Laura... Is it no good? \SE[63]Look... Just the
tip... Just the tip, that's all...

This is the 'Yuri Branch'. Let's choose the development after
this.

\SE[44]Don't be so selfish. \SE[55]Because I am Lunaroa's lover.
[2]I want to wait until she awakens.

\SE[46]Mmm... I guess it was impossible. \!\SE[63]Do you know? At
night, when I have too much energy, I comfort myself alone.

\SE[82]How do you know...!!? \!\SE[71]No, I-I'm not doing
anything like that!!
\SE[2]Well, that's fine. \SE[0]Then let's sleep together today.

\SE[66]I'll give you the right to use me as a body pillow.
\.Because I'm warm, you can sleep well...

\SE[66]If you can, please stroke my head occasionally. When you
do that, I can sleep well. It's because of me. \SE[8]If it's just
that... it's okay, right?
\SE[44] (Because I'm trying to hide my awkwardness...)
